WEBVTT

00:00:00.099 --> 00:00:25.159
Subtitle Provide by dramacool.asia Translator [Admin.@YNG]

00:00:56.280 --> 00:01:00.260
=The Demon=

00:01:00.580 --> 00:01:03.250
=Episode 15=

00:01:03.479 --> 00:01:04.719
Buns for sale!

00:01:05.120 --> 00:01:07.439
Freshly steamed bun!

00:01:07.799 --> 00:01:08.640
Let me see.

00:01:08.640 --> 00:01:10.200
Steaming hot buns!

00:01:10.200 --> 00:01:11.560
Fresh buns!

00:01:11.560 --> 00:01:12.439
Let me try.

00:01:12.439 --> 00:01:13.319
Come and try them.

00:01:13.560 --> 00:01:15.319
The buns look delicious,

00:01:15.319 --> 00:01:16.120
Dayao.

00:01:17.079 --> 00:01:18.920
Since when do you like eating buns?

00:01:19.799 --> 00:01:22.760
Honestly, I'd like to eat one right now.

00:01:23.840 --> 00:01:25.200
It's my fault

00:01:25.599 --> 00:01:27.640
for dragging you along.

00:01:27.680 --> 00:01:28.439
Maybe

00:01:28.439 --> 00:01:29.680
I'm not suited

00:01:29.680 --> 00:01:31.519
for this guardian post.

00:01:32.680 --> 00:01:33.640
It's nothing.

00:01:33.640 --> 00:01:34.760
When I master

00:01:34.760 --> 00:01:36.519
the spell to eat once
and stay full ten times,

00:01:36.519 --> 00:01:37.480
this is just a small matter.

00:01:38.040 --> 00:01:38.719
Come on!

00:01:38.719 --> 00:01:40.510
Something is happening
at the Shen Residence today.

00:01:40.690 --> 00:01:41.879
They're handing out wedding sweets.

00:01:41.879 --> 00:01:42.799
Let's go see.

00:01:42.799 --> 00:01:44.319
- Shen Residence?
- Shen Residence?

00:01:44.840 --> 00:01:45.719
I'm coming too.

00:01:46.599 --> 00:01:47.760
Dayao, wait for me.

00:01:49.760 --> 00:01:53.439
They're coming out.

00:01:53.920 --> 00:01:55.840
Such a perfect match.

00:01:56.319 --> 00:01:57.359
(Shen Residence)
They are truly made for each other.

00:01:57.359 --> 00:01:58.040
Look!

00:01:58.040 --> 00:02:00.280
Young Master Shen and Princess Huaiyang
are getting engaged.

00:02:01.040 --> 00:02:02.159
What a fine couple.

00:02:02.159 --> 00:02:03.560
A match made in heaven.

00:02:03.879 --> 00:02:04.760
Thank you, everyone.

00:02:04.760 --> 00:02:05.920
We're giving out candies.

00:02:06.079 --> 00:02:07.680
Oh, thank you!

00:02:07.760 --> 00:02:10.719
Thank you, Your Highness.

00:02:11.360 --> 00:02:12.319
Thank you, Your Highness.

00:02:12.599 --> 00:02:13.879
Over here! Over here!

00:02:13.879 --> 00:02:14.919
I want some too!

00:02:16.520 --> 00:02:17.719
Over here!

00:02:18.280 --> 00:02:19.080
Over here.

00:02:20.840 --> 00:02:21.639
Thank you.

00:02:21.639 --> 00:02:23.280
I want some too.

00:02:23.759 --> 00:02:25.400
They're such a fine pair.

00:02:25.400 --> 00:02:25.599
That's right.

00:02:25.599 --> 00:02:26.319
Over here.

00:02:26.439 --> 00:02:27.120
This is mine.

00:02:27.120 --> 00:02:28.159
It wasn't easy for me to get this.

00:02:36.250 --> 00:02:39.675
(Shen Residence)

00:02:40.240 --> 00:02:40.960
Rong Momo.

00:02:40.960 --> 00:02:41.680
Let me have some.

00:02:41.759 --> 00:02:43.080
Can you tell me

00:02:43.520 --> 00:02:45.039
what "engaged" means?

00:02:45.439 --> 00:02:48.280
It means the man

00:02:48.319 --> 00:02:49.400
and woman fancy each other.

00:02:49.400 --> 00:02:50.719
Speak so I can understand.

00:02:51.479 --> 00:02:52.800
It means Mr. Shen

00:02:52.800 --> 00:02:53.680
will now

00:02:53.680 --> 00:02:55.240
be the Princess's husband.

00:03:03.240 --> 00:03:04.759
Cheater.

00:03:06.000 --> 00:03:06.800
Dayao,

00:03:06.960 --> 00:03:08.400
don't go near them.

00:03:08.400 --> 00:03:10.199
There are too many people.

00:03:10.199 --> 00:03:11.520
We need to think this through

00:03:11.520 --> 00:03:12.639
and discuss this.

00:03:12.759 --> 00:03:13.560
Wangchen,

00:03:14.360 --> 00:03:15.680
I'm a little tired.

00:03:15.960 --> 00:03:17.159
Let's go back.

00:03:18.240 --> 00:03:19.039
All right.

00:03:19.719 --> 00:03:20.759
You must be tired, Your Highness.

00:03:21.439 --> 00:03:22.479
Not at all.

00:03:26.275 --> 00:03:28.412
(Shen Residence)

00:04:12.879 --> 00:04:13.680
Master,

00:04:13.719 --> 00:04:15.039
I sense demonic activity

00:04:15.039 --> 00:04:16.279
beyond this bridge.

00:04:16.639 --> 00:04:17.439
We're already too late.

00:04:18.079 --> 00:04:19.040
I've already checked.

00:04:19.040 --> 00:04:21.519
A family of four has been drained of their essence,

00:04:21.759 --> 00:04:22.759
not a bone left.

00:04:23.160 --> 00:04:24.920
We must keep this quiet,

00:04:25.480 --> 00:04:28.040
or Moyuan City will fall into panic.

00:04:29.560 --> 00:04:30.360
Yes, Master.

00:04:31.319 --> 00:04:33.199
I'm afraid
there's big trouble in the city.

00:04:33.720 --> 00:04:35.399
Then I'll report to the City Lord

00:04:35.480 --> 00:04:36.560
and organize a hunt.

00:04:36.560 --> 00:04:37.279
No.

00:04:37.439 --> 00:04:38.680
Do not startle the enemy.

00:04:39.199 --> 00:04:41.079
Leave this to me.

00:04:57.839 --> 00:04:59.399
Dayao, you're here again.

00:05:00.680 --> 00:05:02.439
Why don't we leave this place?

00:05:04.199 --> 00:05:05.600
The people of Moyuan City

00:05:05.600 --> 00:05:06.600
are too complicated.

00:05:06.600 --> 00:05:08.319
This place is simply not for us.

00:05:08.519 --> 00:05:09.879
Let's return to the Demon Fort.

00:05:10.199 --> 00:05:11.480
That's our true home.

00:05:11.680 --> 00:05:13.319
Don't talk to me.

00:05:13.680 --> 00:05:14.839
I need to think.

00:05:16.160 --> 00:05:17.240
At a time like this,

00:05:17.240 --> 00:05:18.519
what's there to think about?

00:05:18.800 --> 00:05:20.639
Shen Wangchen already made his choice.

00:05:20.800 --> 00:05:21.680
Who does he think he is?

00:05:21.680 --> 00:05:23.079
It's making me furious.

00:05:23.240 --> 00:05:24.879
And that Jiang Li too.

00:05:26.319 --> 00:05:27.120
Forget it.

00:05:27.879 --> 00:05:29.360
I don't need Jiang Li either.

00:05:29.360 --> 00:05:30.519
Let them have whoever they want.

00:05:30.800 --> 00:05:31.839
We'll go back to the Demon Fort.

00:05:33.399 --> 00:05:35.079
But I can't shake the feeling

00:05:35.439 --> 00:05:37.439
that Shen Wangchen isn't like that.

00:05:37.800 --> 00:05:38.639
Why do you think he...

00:05:50.240 --> 00:05:52.000
Why do you carry red beans with you?

00:05:57.879 --> 00:05:59.519
They are as hard as stones.

00:05:59.519 --> 00:06:01.839
Yet, you've turned them
into something so soft and sweet.

00:06:02.000 --> 00:06:03.160
Because red beans are said

00:06:03.240 --> 00:06:04.839
to be the fruit of longing.

00:06:08.040 --> 00:06:09.360
I learn something new.

00:06:10.000 --> 00:06:10.800
(Then)

00:06:11.079 --> 00:06:12.480
(can I have another bowl?)

00:06:15.879 --> 00:06:16.680
(As much as you like.)

00:06:19.560 --> 00:06:20.839
I trust him.

00:06:55.639 --> 00:06:56.720
Why are you here?

00:06:57.000 --> 00:06:57.800
Momo?

00:06:57.800 --> 00:06:58.920
I've finally found you.

00:06:59.199 --> 00:07:00.720
Shouldn't you be enjoying

00:07:00.720 --> 00:07:02.079
the Princess's riches

00:07:02.079 --> 00:07:02.879
with Shen Wangchen?

00:07:03.439 --> 00:07:04.240
Momo.

00:07:05.600 --> 00:07:07.199
You must be starving these few days.

00:07:07.680 --> 00:07:09.360
Look what I brought.

00:07:11.560 --> 00:07:13.120
What took you so long?

00:07:13.399 --> 00:07:14.839
I've gone days

00:07:14.839 --> 00:07:16.560
without a proper meal.

00:07:18.000 --> 00:07:19.079
Forgive me, Momo.

00:07:19.920 --> 00:07:21.560
I know you have suffered
these past few days.

00:07:22.319 --> 00:07:23.680
That wretched princess

00:07:23.759 --> 00:07:24.879
never lets us out of her sight.

00:07:25.079 --> 00:07:26.720
I barely managed to sneak away.

00:07:28.160 --> 00:07:29.079
I'm sorry.

00:07:29.439 --> 00:07:30.319
Eat first.

00:07:34.319 --> 00:07:35.120
Here.

00:07:38.240 --> 00:07:39.199
Slowly, don't choke yourself.

00:07:43.920 --> 00:07:47.199
So, does this mean
Mr. Shen and the Princess

00:07:47.199 --> 00:07:49.519
will always be together?

00:07:49.720 --> 00:07:51.319
Who knows
what Young Master truly thinks?

00:07:52.199 --> 00:07:53.759
But I can't stand that Princess.

00:07:55.600 --> 00:07:56.639
Then does that mean

00:07:57.240 --> 00:07:59.000
we can't

00:07:59.000 --> 00:08:00.199
be together anymore?

00:08:00.439 --> 00:08:01.959
I thought

00:08:02.319 --> 00:08:04.600
if Dayao and Mr. Shen

00:08:04.600 --> 00:08:06.120
could get married,

00:08:06.879 --> 00:08:08.639
then maybe we could too.

00:08:09.759 --> 00:08:10.560
We?

00:08:16.360 --> 00:08:17.480
If you don't want it, just say so.

00:08:17.720 --> 00:08:18.959
You didn't have to run!

00:08:32.519 --> 00:08:33.320
Momo.

00:08:33.399 --> 00:08:34.200
Leave me alone.

00:08:34.320 --> 00:08:35.440
I don't want to see you.

00:08:36.320 --> 00:08:37.120
I'm sorry.

00:08:37.399 --> 00:08:38.879
I should've proposed first.

00:08:39.200 --> 00:08:40.000
Momo, look.

00:08:40.480 --> 00:08:42.039
This is all I own.

00:08:42.360 --> 00:08:43.279
It may not be much.

00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:44.919
But I promise

00:08:45.240 --> 00:08:46.440
I'll cook

00:08:46.440 --> 00:08:47.320
whatever you want to eat.

00:08:47.639 --> 00:08:48.440
I'm serious.

00:08:48.480 --> 00:08:49.159
I'll give everything

00:08:49.159 --> 00:08:50.399
just to make you smile.

00:08:53.679 --> 00:08:54.480
The truth is,

00:08:55.679 --> 00:08:57.519
since the very first moment I saw you,

00:09:01.279 --> 00:09:03.919
I was already in love.

00:09:14.240 --> 00:09:17.799
What if

00:09:17.799 --> 00:09:19.039
Mr. Shen doesn't agree?

00:09:19.039 --> 00:09:19.879
Who cares?

00:09:20.559 --> 00:09:21.360
Momo,

00:09:22.000 --> 00:09:23.559
let's spend our lives together.

00:09:24.159 --> 00:09:24.960
What do you say?

00:09:25.559 --> 00:09:26.679
Of course!

00:09:26.679 --> 00:09:29.525
♪Love is hard to comprehend
in this world♪

00:09:30.950 --> 00:09:34.775
♪Yearning for love feels the longest♪

00:09:35.937 --> 00:09:41.487
♪Who comes with me on my long journey?♪

00:09:41.487 --> 00:09:46.150
♪Where can I rest
after picking up the cold branches?♪

00:09:46.375 --> 00:09:52.225
♪I'm willing to trade all my smiles
from the past♪

00:09:52.320 --> 00:09:53.320
Wangchen, look.

00:09:53.840 --> 00:09:55.039
The garden is in full bloom

00:09:55.399 --> 00:09:56.759
for you.

00:09:57.360 --> 00:09:58.600
Just like my heart,

00:09:59.279 --> 00:10:00.679
beating only for you.

00:10:02.080 --> 00:10:03.310
You're flattering me, Your Highness.

00:10:03.720 --> 00:10:05.320
These flowers are nature's beauty.

00:10:05.519 --> 00:10:06.440
It has nothing to do with me.

00:10:09.039 --> 00:10:09.840
Wangchen.

00:10:13.240 --> 00:10:15.159
From the moment I first saw you,

00:10:15.159 --> 00:10:15.759
I...

00:10:15.759 --> 00:10:16.480
Your Highness.

00:10:17.559 --> 00:10:19.320
Don't forget I suffer from a strange illness.

00:10:21.559 --> 00:10:22.360
But...

00:10:23.720 --> 00:10:24.519
But...

00:10:29.120 --> 00:10:30.799
But I can't be bothered
with all that anymore.

00:10:40.512 --> 00:10:42.362
(Shen Residence)

00:10:51.307 --> 00:10:54.970
♪Where did I lose my direction?♪

00:10:55.282 --> 00:10:57.695
♪Only emptiness is left♪

00:10:59.082 --> 00:11:02.857
♪Restless, sleepless, we part ways♪

00:11:02.995 --> 00:11:05.720
♪As sorrow slowly grows within♪

00:11:06.820 --> 00:11:10.307
♪Tears can't heal, smiles still ache♪

00:11:10.682 --> 00:11:13.932
♪Because my heart's with you♪

00:11:14.557 --> 00:11:19.382
♪Your gaze melted the haze♪

00:11:20.832 --> 00:11:27.695
♪Waiting so long for your return♪

00:11:28.557 --> 00:11:35.845
♪The setting sun reminds me of you♪

00:11:36.345 --> 00:11:41.257
♪If the clear sky is torn
by storm and rain one day♪

00:11:41.607 --> 00:11:44.407
♪Tears will flow♪

00:11:45.545 --> 00:11:51.182
♪I will still wait here with no regrets♪

00:11:51.857 --> 00:11:59.045
♪Waiting so long for your return♪

00:11:59.582 --> 00:12:06.732
♪The setting sun reminds me of you♪

00:12:07.332 --> 00:12:12.020
♪In the amber desert,
you turn away with tears in your eyes♪

00:12:12.382 --> 00:12:15.807
♪I'll welcome you back in a red dress♪

00:12:16.420 --> 00:12:22.307
♪Waiting forever with no regrets♪

00:12:24.020 --> 00:12:31.595
♪Waiting forever with no regrets♪